    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slapstick Bosses is a heavily stylized boss fighting game, with a sole focus on gameplay and comedy. Explore the game's wacky world and all the outlandish humor it has to offer.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each boss is completely unique, offering different playstyles throughout. What they do have in common is their 3 difficulties, ranging from challenging yet calm to blood-curdlingly difficult; as well as challenges for each, modified bosses that provide a new way to play each boss. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each boss defeat will earn you more of the game's currency: <strong>Bits</strong>, which can be used to buy a plethora of cosmetics. The harder the difficulty, the more bits you'll earn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmetics come in the form of heads. Both swappable and stylish, these bad boys are always worth the price.<br><br>Get trailers and updates on my channel: </p>",
